messages.message:
Hi all, I’ve added an explicit checklist to the PR template on GitHub (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/9840)

1. Let’s have 100% coverage on the labeling and Release Notes Text.

One non-obvious note: If you have a change that is a “Bug fix” but you don’t want it to show up in the Release Notes, add the “Internal” label as a second label to the PR
I haven't gotten the release notes 100% finished up yet on my end - I'll make sure they're ready tonight tho
